		</div>
	</div>
</div>My main issue right now is that, after leaving Kingsmouth town behind I would have appreciated a change of scenery, but the Savage Coast is essentially more of the same and a quick peek into the Blue Mountains showed no sweeping changes, either. Missions seem diverse enough for me so far, though it's slightly frustrating that you can never be sure which investigations can be completed without internet research. A bummer if you're trying to avoid spoiler sites.<br />
<br />
<div class="bbcode_container">
	<div class="bbcode_quote">
		<div class="quote_container">
